  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add shallots and cook until fragrant, about 2 minutes.",
    "Add garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add sambal oelek and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add fish sauce and lime juice, stir to combine.",
    "Add green chilies, lemongrass, and galangal. Cook for 2 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add white asparagus and cook until tender, about 4-6 minutes.",
    "Stir in beurre-monte and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Season with pepper and chili flakes to taste.",
    "Garnish with cilantro and serve immediately."
